  "texts": [
    "In human-AI-perceived-as-human interactions, decision changes occurred at a rate of 16.84% (±1.2% s.e.)",
    "when there was a disagreement, compared with a mere 0.2% (±0.05% s.e.)",
    "when agreeing (permutation test comparing the two: P < 0.001; d = 1.22; 95% CI = 0.13 to 0.20).",
    "Similarly, for the humanhuman-perceived-as-AI condition, decision changes were observed in 31.84% (±2.5% s.e.)",
    "when disagreement existed, compared with 0.4% (±0.1% s.e.)"
  ],
